Name: tint2
Version: 17.0.2
Release: alt2
Summary: Simple panel/taskbar made for modern x window managers

Group: Graphical desktop/Other
License: GPLv2
Url: https://gitlab.com/o9000/tint2

Source: %name-%version.tar
